    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯精炼燃料出货量因柴油流量减少而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/russia-s-refined-fuel-shipments-edge-down-as-diesel-flows-shrink</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于柴油出口减少，俄罗斯石油产品出口在 11 月份因更多炼油厂结束季节性维护而出现反弹，上周出口略有下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/russia-s-refined-fuel-shipments-edge-down-as-diesel-flows-shrink</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 10:05:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Access Bank 将收购 Bidvest Bank，寻求扩大业务范围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/nigeria-s-access-bank-to-buy-bidvest-bank-as-it-seeks-bigger-footprint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Access Bank Plc 已提出以约 28 亿兰特（1.59 亿美元）收购 Bidvest Bank Holdings Ltd，以帮助尼日利亚这家资产规模最大的银行在南非扩张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/nigeria-s-access-bank-to-buy-bidvest-bank-as-it-seeks-bigger-footprint</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 10:00:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚、保加利亚获准进入欧盟免护照区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/romania-and-bulgaria-win-full-access-to-passport-free-eu-area</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚和保加利亚将于明年完全进入欧盟免护照区，这一历史性决定将有助于提振这两个国家陷入困境的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/romania-and-bulgaria-win-full-access-to-passport-free-eu-area</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 08:54:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
